2.text: It's the Sinhala and Tamil new year. The students brought festive food to school. They arranged the festive food table. There were milkrice, kokis, christmas cake, laddu, watalappan and banana. Nisal, Tony, Meena and Navaz talked about the festive food.

4.text: It's white in colour and square in shape. We use rice and coconut milk to make it. We make it for our new year. What is it?

5.text: It is sweet and brown in colour with a white icing top. It's square in shape. We use fruits to make it. What is it?
